sentences: Merve Çağıran (born 10 November 1992) is a Turkish actress.
In 2010, she made her television debut with a role in Tek Türkiye.
After appearing in various TV series, her main breakthrough occurred in 2016 with Aşk Laftan Anlamaz
In 2018, she was honored at the Golden Butterfly Awards with the Shining Star award.
